107 'IFCHECK MANA'~
&r*-------------------------------------------------------------------*

          &GEXAMPLE:   &cif mana($n) > 100
                     'You're low on mana, $n.

      &GDESCRIPTION:   &cThe MANA ifcheck is used to determine the
                     amount of mana the target has.

 &r*-------------------------------------------------------------------*

