&r*-------------------------------------------------------------------*

        &GEXAMPLE:       &cif mobinvislevel($i) == 50
                       'I'm invisible to all under lvl 50 

    &GDESCRIPTION:       &cThe MOBINVISLEVEL is used to determine
                       the level the target is invisible to. 

 &r*-------------------------------------------------------------------*

