                          how many PCs the target has logged in. Also
                          applies to MOBs, objects, rooms.

&r*-------------------------------------------------------------------*

    &YSEE ALSO: &wMPEDIT, OPEDIT, RPEDIT, IFCHECKS, IFCHECKS2, IFCHECKS3

~

