&cPlease check out help files &OBuilding&c, &OImmlaws&c, and &OImmlaws2&c.
&rUPDATE:&PAs of June 29th, 2000 we have extended the levels.  They now range
from newbie 1 to avatar 90-100, and immortal levels 101 to 115.  We have set
everyone to their new level accordingly with what they were before, and insured
that their prototype area (if applicable) remains.  If you find any problem
that you believe to be related to this transition, please contact a high level
immortal ASAP.
